

edit celestia.pro to your system 

Requires lua5.1 and lua5.1-devel( or -dev) 
the rest are the current versions in most linux distros 
-- fedora warnning as is NORMAL with fedora some lib's might be TOO NEW 

Requires qt5 development tools and qmake-qt5 
( i link qmake-qt5 OR qmake-qt4 to qmake as needed )

edit the "celestia.pro " to add your cspice location and your install location 


mkdir build
cd build
qmake ..
( or  qmake prefix=/usr .. ) 
make
make install 

----------------

qmake prefix=/DATA/SUSE/Qt5Celestia ..

